&lt;li&gt;Create online sales funnels in Salesforce CRM through record creation and management and keep funnels up to date with new wins.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain active relationships with network representatives to be at the forefront of upcoming changes, trends, tactics, and tools in order to effectively navigate our campaigns through these updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with multiple departments to drive marketing projects from idea to completion and then through testing/optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regularly analyze and provide improvements for the customer experience throughout the sales funnel, from day one acquisition to 90 day customer retention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform audits of web analytics implementations and make recommendations to ensure accurate tracking is in place.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
