&lt;li&gt;1-3 year of experience in Digital Marketing preferably within Digital Acquisition/ Performance Marketing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience optimizing sales funnels via A/B testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience scaling and maintaining ad campaigns while hitting Key Performance Metrics &amp;amp; goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s Degree (preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 years of Digital Acquisition/ Performance Marketing (preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
